        {
            "id": "tradingview:e22f4dfa53903:0",
            "title": "Lamb Weston Holdings FY 2026: Revenue $6.61B, EPS $2.08— 10-K Summary",
            "description": "<div class=\"body-Xl9a4Ubk body-nzzZVyQ3 content-nzzZVyQ3\"><div class=\"symbolsContainer-uFduEtAF logosContainer-diQOvrPB\" data-no-swipe=\"true\"></div><div><span><p class=\"\"><span>Lamb Weston Holdings, Inc. reported fiscal 2026 results with revenue of $6.61B, up modestly from $6.45B a year earlier, while net income and diluted EPS declined to $290M and $2.08, respectively, on a year-over-year basis.</span></p><p class=\"\"><strong class=\"root-Tkn6WL2y\"><span>Financial Highlights</span></strong></p><div class=\"tableContainer-VG8_37yK\"><table class=\"table-VG8_37yK\" data-no-swipe=\"true\"><tbody><tr><td><span>Metric</span></td><td><span>Current year</span></td><td><span>Prior year</span></td><td><span>YoY change</span></td></tr><tr><td><span>Revenue¹</span></td><td><span>$6.61B</span></td><td><span>$6.45B</span></td><td><span>2.5%</span></td></tr><tr><td><span>Net income²</span></td><td><span>$290M</span></td><td><span>$357.2M</span></td><td><span>(18.8%)</span></td></tr><tr><td><span>Diluted EPS³</span></td><td><span>$2.08</span></td><td><span>$2.5</span></td><td><span>(16.8%)</span></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p class=\"\"><em><span>¹ Reported as “Net sales”. ² Reported as “Net income”. ³ Reported as “Diluted earnings per share”.</span></em></p><p class=\"\"><strong class=\"root-Tkn6WL2y\"><span>Business Highlights</span></strong></p><ul class=\"list-bmN0_SHH list--padded-bmN0_SHH\"><li class=\"listItem-bmN0_SHH\"><span>Revenue growth was driven by 7% volume growth and the benefit of a 53rd week.</span></li><li class=\"listItem-bmN0_SHH\"><span>North America showed strong volume and share gains; growth in APAC and Latin America offset softness in EMEA.</span></li><li class=\"listItem-bmN0_SHH\"><span>Brand momentum continued with customer retention and new contract wins, notably in North America.</span></li><li class=\"listItem-bmN0_SHH\"><span>Cost Savings Program surpassed a $100M year-one milestone, reducing cost per pound and SG&amp;A.</span></li><li class=\"listItem-bmN0_SHH\"><span>Company completed major capacity expansions, including opening a new Argentina facility, lowering capital intensity.</span></li></ul><p class=\"\"><span>Original SEC Filing: </span><a class=\"link-zw5jRdec icon-zw5jRdec\" href=\"https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/1679273/000167927326000026/lw-20260531.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Lamb Weston Holdings, Inc. [ LW ] - 10-K - Jul. 24, 2026</a></p><section class=\"variant-secondary-Gmpzg_mv disclaimer-PlF2Sa64\"><b class=\"heading-wrapper-Gmpzg_mv\"><span class=\"heading-Gmpzg_mv\">Disclaimer</span></b><div class=\"content-Gmpzg_mv link-with-underline-Gmpzg_mv\"><span>This is an AI-powered summary. It may contain inaccuracies. Consider verifying important information with the source. Please note this summary is solely based on documents filed with the SEC.</span></div></section></span></div></div>",
            "link": "https://www.tradingview.com/news/tradingview:e22f4dfa53903:0-lamb-weston-holdings-fy-2026-revenue-6-61b-eps-2-08-10-k-summary/",
